  "architecture_summary": "This is a survey of Transformer models in computer vision. It organizes the literature around self-attention design space and vision tasks, covering single-head and multi-head Transformer variants, their architectural differences, and their applications across recognition, detection, segmentation, generation, multi-modal learning, video understanding, low-shot learning, clustering, and 3D analysis.",
